trans-unit.source: Provides methods for a subscription service to manage subscriptions for a workflow runtime.
trans-unit.target: 구독 서비스에서 워크플로 런타임에 대한 구독을 관리하는 데 사용할 수 있는 메서드를 제공합니다.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.WorkflowSubscriptionService> is the base class for any subscription service classes used in the Workflow Foundation (WF).
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.WorkflowSubscriptionService>는 WF(Workflow Foundation)에 사용되는 구독 서비스 클래스의 기본 클래스입니다.

trans-unit.source: When you inherit from <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.WorkflowSubscriptionService" />, you must override the following members: <see cref="M:System.Workflow.Activities.WorkflowSubscriptionService.CreateSubscription(System.Workflow.Activities.MessageEventSubscription)" /> and <see cref="M:System.Workflow.Activities.WorkflowSubscriptionService.DeleteSubscription(System.Guid)" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.WorkflowSubscriptionService" />에서 상속하는 경우 <see cref="M:System.Workflow.Activities.WorkflowSubscriptionService.CreateSubscription(System.Workflow.Activities.MessageEventSubscription)" /> 및 <see cref="M:System.Workflow.Activities.WorkflowSubscriptionService.DeleteSubscription(System.Guid)" /> 멤버를 재정의해야 합니다.

trans-unit.source: When implemented in a derived class, initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.WorkflowSubscriptionService" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 파생 클래스에서 구현되는 경우에는 <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.WorkflowSubscriptionService" /> 클래스의 새 인스턴스를 초기화합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.MessageEventSubscription" /> that the workflow runtime created.

When overridden in a derived class, notifies the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.WorkflowSubscriptionService" /> that the workflow runtime created the specified <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.MessageEventSubscription" />.
trans-unit.target: 파생 클래스에서 재정의되는 경우 지정된 <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.WorkflowSubscriptionService" />을 워크플로 런타임에서 만들었음을 <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.MessageEventSubscription" />에 알려줍니다.

trans-unit.source: The GUID of the subscription that the workflow runtime deleted.

When overridden in a derived class, notifies the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.WorkflowSubscriptionService" /> that the workflow runtime deleted the subscription associated with the specified GUID.
trans-unit.target: 파생 클래스에서 재정의되는 경우 워크플로 런타임에서 지정된 GUID와 연관된 구독을 삭제했음을 <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.WorkflowSubscriptionService" />에 알려줍니다.
